---
title: Glazed Chicken Thighs with Sheet Pan Roasted Veggies
description: This is a classic no-fuss dinner for any night of the week! Chicken thighs get coated in a balsamic glaze, then roasted with a medley of seasonal veggies to make a sheet pan dinner that will have everyone smiling!
